{"tid":1526173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場機場機場","createTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T05:04:58.000Z","uid":14092,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"8a7491a54460fce201bcf03afb7e9a72c4e96f61","tid":1526173,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"901 機場攻略<br />\n麻煩大家用盡所有方法傳開佢<br />\n<br />\n- 準時到機場，唔係一點先出門口<br />\n- 衣着同裝備冇任何限制，最緊要保護自己<br />\n- 集合地點：機場巴士總站(暢達路)<br />\n- 測試方法：排隊戰術，見到有隊就排；利用人數優勢，唔好單獨行事<br />\n- 唔好同任何遊客有肢體碰撞<br />\n- 去機場：以巴士為優先，機場快線集中係香港同青衣站上車<br />\n- 已經準備左幾套應變方案，根據現場情況隨時轉變，要密切留意住 901 機場 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=ea633f2c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a>"},{"pid":"236bf697dbf154c2fc9b4b4712e6c9874f721c7c","tid":1526173,"uid":170281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee27e4ab7a8e3ecafe20ff26097b48584b2bab3f","tid":1526173,"uid":117282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20e571c01a4969cd501737284aed455916ac6439","tid":1526173,"uid":53922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:01.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"8934bce2019c20e99115a99cff1a97b21e482843","tid":1526173,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:23.000Z","msg":"人手置頂機場post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上熱門"},{"pid":"7100905614072b6c174c25a49f5b4e75d6f40e0e","tid":1526173,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站 拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n明明你地有能力 又咁容易 點解大家仲未收狗鐵皮?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1523278\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1523278</a>"},{"pid":"08b56c9795ff38df85cf1dad4488f436f763f59d","tid":1526173,"uid":170281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:37:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"276d5be4db6038caebae35fd31fd8d8a83e43c19","tid":1526173,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:38:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"52a4fe5df5bc6188e01a8dc64d2caa984c4d4519","tid":1526173,"uid":59703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:38:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a97de2d660a30495840f78e6da49d93859589281","tid":1526173,"uid":8873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:38:53.000Z","msg":"所有機場post俾人洗緊下面"},{"pid":"6e808319506cc70a8b64e4bab820fabe774b1c11","tid":1526173,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:39:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1e54fa65a9f8d736f97bdf6d13c639d1dda845ac","tid":1526173,"uid":183950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb02f28492d1bd69089c4559c674404983b6ece","tid":1526173,"uid":14092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"E線 E11 E21 E22 E23 E22A E32 E42 就「一號及二號客運大樓」落 呢個係機場下層 可落車<br />\nE33 E34A E34B E33P就搭到總站<br />\nE41要T1落 轉接駁巴<br />\n所有A線搭到 機場（地面運輸中心）巴士總站"},{"pid":"0c40f93579c2435a79850a81f80ecf0cd4fd89ee","tid":1526173,"uid":28281